---
---

<section
  class="damodaran-section"
  aria-labelledby="damodaran-heading"
  style="padding: 6rem clamp(1.5rem, 6vw, 6rem); position: relative; z-index: 1;"
>
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: center;">

    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="section-label">Featured Programme</span>
      <span class="gold-rule" style="display:block; margin-top: 0.75rem;"></span>
      <h2
        id="damodaran-heading"
        style="
          font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
          font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
          font-weight: 700;
          color: #fff;
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
          line-height: 1.15;
        "
      >
        Aswath Damodaran<br />
        <span style="color: var(--gold); font-style: italic;">Workshop Series</span>
      </h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); line-height: 1.85; font-size: 0.96rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        The Aswath Damodaran workshop is a series of seminars and workshops led by the renowned finance professor and author. Designed to help attendees master value investing, capital markets, financial modeling, and valuation — drawing from Damodaran's unique perspective and practical insights. Held annually in both online and in-person formats on our global platform.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://www.idealsnetwork.com/business-valuation-with-aswath-damodaran"
        class="btn-gold"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        See All Editions
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Decorative card -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="position: relative;">
      <div
        style="
          border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
          padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
          position: relative;
        "
      >
        <div
          style="
            position: absolute;
            top: -1px; left: 2rem;
            width: 60px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--gold);
          "
        ></div>
        <p
          style="
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
          "
        >
          "The greatest risk is not taking one — understanding value is the foundation of every great investment."
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem;">
          <span
            style="
              font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
              font-size: 1.1rem;
              font-weight: 600;
              color: var(--gold);
            "
          >Aswath Damodaran</span>
          <span style="font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;">
            Professor of Finance, NYU Stern School of Business
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative corner -->
        <div
          style="
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 1.5rem;
            right: 1.5rem;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-right: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
          "
        ></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Next event card -->
      <div
        style="
          background: var(--gold);
          padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: space-between;
          gap: 1rem;
          margin-top: -1px;
        "
      >
        <div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(12,27,51,0.7); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">Next Edition</div>
          <div style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy);">
            Singapore — Nov 12–13, 2026
          </div>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://www.idealsnetwork.com/business-valuation-with-aswath-damodaran-nov-singapore"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          style="
            background: var(--navy);
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            white-space: nowrap;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition: background 0.2s;
          "
        >Register →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section > div { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 2.5rem !important; }
  }
</style>
